highlights.text: “Sailor Song” by Gigi Perez has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 154 days straight.
SZA has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “BMF” is the highest at #36.
“Romance Fdp” by DJ Voltz, Mc Jhey, and FreesTyle Sounds is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #7.
“Yo Vengo De La Nada” by Juan Freer and miguel cornejo is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 10 spots at #81.
